sources.description:
Enemy agent "tap" girl's mind for top secret guided missile plans... as David Harding avenges "diplomatic" murder!
A federal agent (Howard St. John) joins forces with a British lawman (Ron Randell) to foil a spy ring.

Original title: Counterspy Meets Scotland Yard (1950)
This film is available with subtitles in many languages

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/9KhSagCu3R8


Director: Seymour Friedman
Writers: Harold Greene, Phillips Lord
Stars: Howard St. John, Ron Randell, Amanda Blake
Genres: Classics, Film-Noir, Crime, Drama
